review_blob: The name its better than the taste.  All the Bahama beers are similar in taste.  Golden ale that pours like a Bud.  Add lime for better results.
Gold ale.  Better of the Bahama beers.  Add lime for better flavor.  Very similar to a Mexican beer.
$35 a case by the Atlantis in the Bahamas makes this beer taste better than $8 a beer at the resort.  Taste similar to a cheap version of a Mexican beer.  Add lime
